" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/hololive_super_expo_2024_hololive_5th_fes_capture_the_moment.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/hololive_super_expo_2024_hololive_5th_fes_capture_the_moment.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/hololive_super_expo_2024_hololive_5th_fes_capture_the_moment.png" alt="Hololive SUPER EXPO 2024 &amp; Hololive 5th fes. 捕捉瞬间 最新信息发布" class="wp-image-107900"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Hololive SUPER EXPO 2024 &amp; Hololive 5th fes. 捕捉瞬间<br>图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">hololive 超级博览会 2024</h2><p> “hololive SUPER EXPO 2024”是 Hololive Production 的第三届综合活动。</p><p>这次的主题是“hololive Island”，是hololive Productions的艺人居住的“hololive Island”，会有很多展览、舞台、周边商品、美食等内容，让粉丝们能够与人才一起度假体验，是可以的。</p><p>会场分为五个区域，每个区域都有统一的展位。此外，直播期间粉丝投票请求最多的“直播间拍照点”也将展出。继上次之后，现场还可以参加cosplay。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading">关键点</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV87N2AlNp_SN1-ScYCEJDMWGTgldjGPnT0AFn0cXW9KHXPwNAOwHtB-sycechVD2J97B8WCWYMEYG9aAahRlZAhwyf-VxQ4SqclW_NnjnVn-WHabBTflxx4q6XD3LKfUbg0kjgMIKS4J4F6ktUu3mwE1=w1097-h777-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV84VqdVzF0UxCbestFLLy3MlRZD7BrDi1WBW8ECOxfK7opzv9wtVQiS6r5unNGcnsmLgdiS_rhbQ0WPMaV8Z5vch_LT62Wdl67c7DgpLyNveeR-3fRdBODG2dvQT9RJbr-8dUqyKWnC9dOLb87KHE3Vq=w1097-h777-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV87xlQhayKILL5fZau2Epm_lw8sYLwVFwuDjNclXrSUHstlX0P6J4b0I5lHjuWUrXTAtuZs1RQWARfWnGBb7aRMMfM4jyWGOIbW78wCDOWUYPapQ00RoYh0qGzjcwURlLgaFdqEdQByDumJ5b_hNBT1G=w1097-h777-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="ht