</style><h2 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">Hololive 5th fes. 捕捉瞬间</h2><p>《Hololive 5th fes. Capture the Moment》是《Hololive》的第五次整体现场公演，首次在4个舞台上进行。此次，除了hololive第1～第3舞台之外，3月17日还将举办由HoneyWorks制作的舞台“HoneyWorks舞台”。</p><p>主题是[从第一届持续的增长。你珍惜的感情和感情。一个将持续下去的未来。 “捕捉这一刻”选自“我希望人们感受到这一刻”。这也与 Hololive Production 的代表歌曲《Shiny Smily Story》（SSS）的部分歌词相关联， <em>“我想捕捉在这里经常听到的欢呼声，并再次寻找新的光芒</em>。”</p><p>此外，本次现场表演采用了三面舞台进行视觉表达。该公司首次多阶段挑战赛也将引起关注。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading">关键点</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV856tEdP1ThKtSJD0CyJCyEgxY0E64ty94DNZlXg17BmjYx-nEQIHLK4z2F2nmR6qneqdjD6ukLjeOTpQhVAXxm04lneVp1XS89aED57yK2z0FQwDY_4snSoMzDBan-czn5X36DrtWeW9G26SjrjVYYi=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV84bt7xcfvX9BDoaTwubP0kwnm8C8PO4uiHuTfRUaO1rsji2zeHygsGhTsM42Val6gUwuBpFCdgV_Doe2ihb7UMjVypwI7IXyejmj62kN1kwDdqAnqzKwpEUij0Sz1IKR5WDe8hDQZFEjXO2n15hqSS0=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV87FIVIQwy6Zz27f_fxoHYHVE-fXq6y5qz-a4Q9aV4CNtxeCqmCUwqGOyJZJcvfAEgGpO49yfHm0FRgLqNkl46rxDpPcYbywLwNIB06_k4q4Encew-UKkYrwfw0A8Cjw2O7lEfR4IAof7KUlONoGcmCJ=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f38a.png" alt="🎊" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/hololivefesEXPO24?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#hololivefesEXPO24</a>信息<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/